{"id":205764,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":1}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"读者接待室","genre":"","count":"181","ytitle":"","mtitle":"白癜疯可用何药?","ftitle":"","authors":["邵钧"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白癜疯可用何药?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(答)杨家复先生:根据你所述病状，我们大概可诊断为白癜疯(Vitilizo)它的原因，尚未明确；在治疗上，尚无特效药物，不过可试用下药:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)Ro，Pyugall1c Ocld"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4.0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Thiganol 5.0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"75%alcornl ad 30.0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日擦一至二次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)印度热带病研究出品之Lonel.，可用之涂擦点部。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(邵钧医师答)"}]}